    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker pull docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:8.6.0
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker network create elastic
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker run --name es01 --net elastic -p 9200:9200 -it docker.elastic.co/elasticsearch/elasticsearch:8.6.0
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"># 重置相关密码
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">docker exec -it es01 /usr/share/elasticsearch/bin/elasticsearch-reset-password</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="集群">集群</h2>
<p>首先按照单节点安装能跑起来先</p>]]></description>
